title: Plane Xtreme S01E02 - Wing and a Prayer
description:
Plane Xtreme S01E02

Wing and a Prayer

Wings of Eagles Owner Steve Hall sends two of his pilots, Dave Doble and Mike Tidwell, to pick up a pair of used airplanes on the island of Curacao, a Caribbean island off the coast of Venezuela.

Mike and Dave are not happy with the condition of the Cessna Caravans. Despite their concerns, the maintenance crew insists that they have been given the best care.
